## Query Debugging

### In Rails Console

```ruby
# Show SQL for query
Article.where(status: 'published').to_sql

# Explain query plan
Article.where(status: 'published').explain

# Count queries
ActiveRecord::Base.connection.query_cache.size

# Enable query logging
ActiveRecord::Base.logger = Logger.new(STDOUT)

# Benchmark queries
Benchmark.measure { Article.includes(:user).to_a }
```

